//Execution steps 

Initialize database:

bash
python init_db.py
Run the server:

bash
python app.py
Browser extension can call:

GET /barcode/123456789/score - Get scores by barcode

POST /products/5/calculate - Calculate new scores

GET /products/search?q=apple - Search products

Example Responses:
GET /barcode/123456789/score

json
{
  "product": "Organic Apples",
  "barcode": "123456789",
  "scores": {
    "environmental": 85.2,
    "social": 72.5,
    "governance": 68.0,
    "economic": 79.1,
    "overall": 77.8
  },
  "last_updated": "2023-06-15T14:30:00Z"
}
